msgid "‘Evaṃ, devā’ti kho, bhikkhave, so puriso rañño khattiyassa muddhābhisittassa paccassosi. "
msgstr "‘Yes, Your Majesty,’ replied that man. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs12, pts-vp-pli3.67, sc22
msgctxt "dn26:12.1"
msgid "Assosuṃ kho, bhikkhave, manussā: "
msgstr "People heard about this: "

msgctxt "dn26:12.2"
msgid "‘ye kira, bho, paresaṃ adinnaṃ theyyasaṅkhātaṃ ādiyanti, tesaṃ rājā dhanamanuppadetī’ti. "
msgstr "‘It seems the king is paying money to anyone who steals from others!’ "

msgctxt "dn26:12.3"
msgid "Sutvāna tesaṃ etadahosi: "
msgstr "It occurred to them, "

msgctxt "dn26:12.4"
msgid "‘yannūna mayampi paresaṃ adinnaṃ theyyasaṅkhātaṃ ādiyeyyāmā’ti. "
msgstr "‘Why don’t we steal from others?’ "

msgctxt "dn26:12.5"
msgid "Atha kho, bhikkhave, aññataro puriso paresaṃ adinnaṃ theyyasaṅkhātaṃ ādiyi. "
